Package wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.registry

Class DragonTemplateRegistry

java.lang.Object
wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.registry.HashRegistry<DragonTemplate>
wtf.choco.dragoneggdrop.registry.DragonTemplateRegistry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Registry<DragonTemplate>
public final class DragonTemplateRegistry
extends HashRegistry<DragonTemplate>
A special Registry implementation for DragonTemplates. This registry also maintains a weighted collection of templates and provides access to getRandomTemplate() to fetch a random template according to its weighted value.
Author:
Parker Hawke - Choco
